00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:16,640
 The father is the answer.

813
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:19,760
 Our relationship with Jesus is the answer.

814
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,560
 And when I start to remind myself

815
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:24,760
 that because Jesus was so generous with me,

816
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:29,200
 I now wanna live my life to be as generous as I can be.

