00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,240
 I'll do it.

824
00:35:47,240 --> 00:35:50,600
 And that terrifies me because I somehow still believe

825
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:52,480
 that this earth is end game.

826
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:55,680
 But my Bible says that this earth is nothing

827
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:57,400
 compared to what's to come in heaven.

828
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,680
 So when I am fighting greed,

829
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:02,400
 when I am no longer wanting to be generous, what do I do?

