00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:04,040
 I remember heaven.

831
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:05,560
 I remember Jesus.

832
00:36:05,560 --> 00:36:07,760
 I remember the price that he paid.

833
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:11,120
 And that compels me to put myself aside,

834
00:36:11,120 --> 00:36:14,800
 to put my things aside and to make everything

