00:36:17,240 --> 00:36:20,960
 And it's so crazy.

837
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:24,480
 This like view that's so upside down for us,

838
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:26,720
 especially those in America,

839
00:36:26,720 --> 00:36:28,720
 where it's like, hey, life is found

