00:36:39,680 --> 00:36:41,440
 And it may not look like you think,

844
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:44,400
 but that's the point of following a God

845
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,920
 who knows what we truly need.

846
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:52,560
 And so just to recap, I'm done.

847
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:57,320
 I'm done thinking that everything is mine.

848
00:36:57,320 --> 00:37:00,720
 And I'm trusting that everything is God's.

849
00:37:00,720 --> 00:37:03,000
 I'm done thinking that I am enough

