00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,680
 and that I can trust myself.

851
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:06,320
 I'm gonna start trusting God.

852
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:10,240
 And I'm done thinking

853
00:37:10,240 --> 00:37:16,840
 that when I somehow get to this plan for my life,

854
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:20,040
 that when I get enough, it'll satisfy me.

855
00:37:20,040 --> 00:37:21,320
 And I'm gonna start believing

856
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:23,680
 that true life is found in giving,

857
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:27,800
 just like Jesus gave himself for me.

858
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:30,200
 Let's pray.

